<h1>Recursive Repeater</h1>

<p>The output for the <strong>correct</strong> approach is displayed below. The
incorrect (c.q. wrong) approach is executed on a clone of the template to prevent
it from polluting the template, which would cause problems with further tests.</p>

[{section ListWrapper}]

	<ol>

		<!--[{loop MyList}]-->
			<li>
				Level [{replace level}], value: [{replace value}]
				<ol>
					<!--	[{section SubList}][{section SubList end}]		-->
				</ol>
			</li>
		<!--[{loop MyList end}]-->

	</ol>

[{section ListWrapper end}]

<h1>Nested Sections &amp; Includes</h1>

<p>Below, both "Static Include" and "Include Template" should be present.</p>

[{section Test}]

	[{section Iets}]

		[{section Iets}]

			<!--[{include "IncludeStatic.html"}]-->

		[{section Iets end}]

	[{section Iets end}]

	[{section NogIets}]

		[{section Iets}]

			[{condition test_me is false}]
				[{include template "Templates\IncludeTemplate.tp4" as WoeiTemplate}]
			[{condition test_me end}]

			<p style="[{condition lipsum_bold is true local}]font-weight:bold;[{condition lipsum_bold end}]">
				Lorem ipsum inside a section...
			</p>

		[{section Iets end}]

	[{section NogIets end}]

[{section Test end}]

[{include template "Templates\IncludeLocalized.tp4"}]

<p style="[{condition lipsum_bold is true}]font-weight:bold;[{condition lipsum_bold end}]">
	Lorem ipsum in global scope (should be bold)...
</p>

